  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Norcio Properties Inc. Privacy Policy</strong></p>
  <p><em>Last updated on January 1, 2025</em></p>

  <h2>Your Privacy Matters to Us</h2>
  <p>Norcio Properties Inc. is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your information. It is important that you read this Privacy Policy fully.</p>

  <p>This Privacy Policy governs the collection and use of your personally identifiable information by Norcio Properties Inc. on the <a href="https://www.norcioproperties.com">www.norcioproperties.com</a> website and any other website or service we offer...</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Your name and email address</li>
    <li>Your phone number and mailing address, if you provide it</li>
    <li>Your location, if you consent</li>
    <li>Browser, device info, IP address</li>
    <li>Page views and on-site activity</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We may also collect data through interactions with our agents or offices.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use cookies and tracking pixels to personalize and improve your experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some site features may not work properly.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To deliver and improve our services</li>
    <li>For support and communication</li>
    <li>To personalize content and marketing</li>
    <li>To analyze site performance and usage trends</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Information We Share</h2>
  <p>We share your information with trusted service providers and our real estate clients to deliver the services you request. We never sell your data.</p>

  <h2>Legal Disclosures</h2>
  <p>We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect rights, safety, or property.</p>

  <h2>Other Websites</h2>
  <p>We are not responsible for the privacy practices of websites linked to from our services.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If discovered, we will delete the data promptly.</p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information, but no system is 100% secure.</p>

  <h2>Access & Control</h2>
  <p>You can contact us to access, update, or delete your data. EU residents have GDPR rights, including data portability and objection to processing.</p>

  <h2>Email Opt-Out</h2>
  <p>Click “unsubscribe” in any email, visit /user/subscription-preferences/, or email us at <a href="mailto:rob@norcioproperties.com">rob@norcioproperties.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be noted on our website or via email.</p>

